OL,3,C'Extremist' Reform could replace
OL,4,CTories as opposition, veteran MSP warns
OL,6,FVeteran Tory MSP Liz Smith has warned
OL,7,Fthat "extremist" Reform UK could
OL,8,Freplace the Conservatives as
OL,9,FHolyrood's opposition.
OL,11,FThe politician, who is standing down
OL,12,Fafter nearly 20 years at Holyrood,
OL,13,Fadmitted her biggest regret was the
OL,14,Fdecline of the Scottish Tories since
OL,15,FRuth Davidson's leadership led the
OL,16,Fparty to historic success.
OL,18,FAhead of the May election, she
OL,19,Fadmitted her colleagues had concerns
OL,20,Fover how the party would rebuild trust
OL,21,Fwith voters.
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775696638
OL,3,C'Extremist' Reform could replace
OL,4,CTories as opposition, veteran MSP warns
OL,6,FBut she denied her party had shifted
OL,7,Fto the right in the wake of Nigel
OL,8,FFarage's popularity and insisted they
OL,9,Fhad not copied the language and
OL,10,Fbehaviour of Reform, which she
OL,11,Fdescribed as "extremist".
OL,13,F"I don't actually think that's
OL,14,Fcorrect," she told the Press
OL,15,FAssociation, urging voters to look at
OL,16,Fthe party's policies.
OL,18,F"I think the media likes to portray
OL,19,Fthat as correct because they see that
OL,20,Fwe're having to fight Reform."
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@XO]uD@AOUvD@IO]zD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775696638
OL,3,C'Extremist' Reform could replace
OL,4,CTories as opposition, veteran MSP warns
OL,6,FShe added: "This is the very first
OL,7,Ftime we've had the right challenging
OL,8,Fus, and quite an extremist right.
OL,10,F"Therefore, we've had to look at the
OL,11,Freactions on key issues like migration
OL,12,Fand some of the issues to do with
OL,13,Fsocial values, where we're being
OL,14,Fchallenged from the right, and we're
OL,15,Fbeing challenged from the left.
OL,17,F"Do I think that the Conservative
OL,18,FParty in Scotland has moved very far
OL,19,Fto the right? No, I don't."
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@AOUyD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
