SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775696638
OL,3,C'Extremist' Reform could replace
OL,4,CTories as opposition, veteran MSP warns
OL,6,FMs Smith said the new tone adopted by
OL,7,FScottish Tory leader Russell Findlay
OL,8,Freflected "what's happening generally
OL,9,Fin politics".
OL,11,FBut asked about polls showing Reform
OL,12,Fcould be Holyrood's second largest
OL,13,Fparty, she said "that is a worry to
OL,14,Fme", adding: "I'm not breaking
OL,15,Fanybody's confidence by saying there
OL,16,Fare concerns within the Scottish
OL,17,FConservatives about how we rebuild
OL,18,Ftrust with the electorate, because the
OL,19,Fpolls are showing that we are not
OL,20,Fdoing that just now."
OL,26,@pD@KOUqD@LO]uD@QOUvD@CO]vD@NOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
