OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775696638
OL,3,C'Extremist' Reform could replace
OL,4,CTories as opposition, veteran MSP warns
OL,6,FMs Smith said she was filled with
OL,7,Fachievement as an MSP for 19 years,
OL,8,Fhaving recently won cross-party
OL,9,Fsupport for her outdoor education
OL,10,FBill, which she will help implement
OL,11,Feven after leaving frontline politics.
OL,13,FShe was not without regret, however,
OL,14,Ftelling PA: "My biggest regret is that
OL,15,Fthe Conservatives have never been a
OL,16,Fbit stronger.
OL,26,@vD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
