OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775696638
OL,3,C'Extremist' Reform could replace
OL,4,CTories as opposition, veteran MSP warns
OL,6,FThe former teacher urged whoever
OL,7,Fcontrols the Scottish Government in
OL,8,FMay to take warnings about the
OL,9,Fcountry's finances "seriously" amid
OL,10,Freports of a #5 billion financial
OL,11,Fblack hole by 2030.
OL,13,FShe said there were "many people out
OL,14,Fthere who could work but choose not
OL,15,Fto".
OL,17,FSocial security was only part of the
OL,18,Freforms she said are needed to stop
OL,19,Fthe feeling among the public that
OL,20,FHolyrood is not working as well as it
OL,21,Fshould be.
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@^O]uD@UOUwD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
