OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775696638
OL,3,C'Extremist' Reform could replace
OL,4,CTories as opposition, veteran MSP warns
OL,6,FShe also called for committee
OL,7,Fconveners to be elected.
OL,9,FMs Smith said she hoped the next
OL,10,Fintake of MSPs would work to restore a
OL,11,Fmore respectful political culture.
OL,13,F"I would like to see that style of
OL,14,Fpolitics be part of the next
OL,15,FParliament," she said, pointing to the
OL,16,Ftone of the recent Assisted Dying
OL,17,FBill, "rather than the division and
OL,18,Fthe rancour and some of the silliness
OL,19,Fthat we tend to get.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@LO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
