OL,3,C'Extremist' Reform could replace
OL,4,CTories as opposition, veteran MSP warns
OL,6,F"I don't think that's what the public
OL,7,Fwants. I think they want a better
OL,8,Fparliament."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]
